<DOC><DOCNO> ZF32-017-180 </DOCNO><DOCID>11 461 338</DOCID><JOURNAL>InfoWorld  Nov 4 1991 v13 n44 p85(3).andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>DR DOS 6: worthy alternative to MS-DOS 5: Digital's latest addstask switcher, disk management utilities, improved Windowssupport. (Software Review) (Digital Research DR DOS 6.0 operatingsystem)(includes related article on new evaluation score forMicrosoft DOS 5.0) (evaluation)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Glass, Brett.andM;</AUTHOR><TEXT><ABSTRACT>Digital Research Inc's DR DOS 6.0 operating system remains aheadof MS-DOS in feature and functionality, offering a new taskswitcher, better support for Microsoft Windows and hypertext help.andO;A 'DiskMax' set of hard disk utilities provides file compressionand disk caching capabilities.andP;  It uses a licensed version of thepopular Super PC-Kwik cache program and AddStor Inc's SuperStorcompression utility.andP;  There are two ways of recovering deletedfiles: Diskmap takes a picture of the File Allocation Table (FAT)and preserves information needed for file recovery; and Delwatchactually preserves files the user deletes.andP;  There are severallevels of password protection included.andP;  New commands includeMove, which moves files between directories, and Rendir, whichmakes it easy to rename directories.andP;  Memory handling isexcellent; the program frees 624Kbytes of conventional memory on aNorthgate Elegance 386 using its own memory manager.andP;  The userinterface is very good.andP;  Speed is good but is slightly slower thanMS-DOS in CPU-intensive tests.andP;  Compatibility is very good, anddocumentation is excellent.andP;  Setup is good.andP;  Ease of learning andease of use are both very good.andP;  Error handling is satisfactory.andO;Digital Research's support policies are good, and its technicalsupport is satisfactory.andP;  The program earns a score of excellentfor overall value.andM;</ABSTRACT></TEXT><DESCRIPT>Company:   Digital Research Inc. (Products).andO;Product:   DR DOS 6.0 (Operating system) (evaluation).andO;Topic:     Operating systemsEvaluationSystems software.andO;Feature:   illustrationtable.andO;Caption:   Report card. (table)Applications tests. (table)andM;</DESCRIPT></DOC>